  "title": "Medical Assistant (Aesthetic Clinic) #78742",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Medical Aesthetic/ Skincare</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Medical Assistant</strong></li><li>Working Location: Orchard/ Novena</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 Working Days, 44 hrs per week, Close on Sunday & PH</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + Commission + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Support the doctor during the medical aesthetic treatments and procedures.</li><li>Assist with handling and preparing medical equipment throughout sessions.</li><li>Get patients ready for their treatments, including necessary documentation.</li><li>Educate patients on expected recovery time and provide guidance for pre- and post-treatment care.</li><li>Conduct follow-ups with patients after procedures and during review appointments.</li><li>Perform administrative tasks with accuracy and attention to detail.</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and tidiness of the workspace.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>At least 1 year of hands-on experience in the aesthetic, skincare, or beauty industry.</li><li>With basic computer skills.</li><li>Team player with the ability to work independently when needed.</li><li>Candidates with CIDESCO, CIBTAC, ITEC, or Nursing qualification is an added advantage.</li><li>Passionate about customer service.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#78742 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
